```
models/
  v001/
    ensemble.pkl
    feature_columns.json
    metrics.json
    trained_on.json       # date range of training data
  v002/
    ...
  current -> v003/        # Symlink to active version
```

## Guardrails
- Always use TimeSeriesSplit — never random split on temporal data
- Always validate new model against holdout before deploying
- Always maintain fallback to rule-based if ML server is unreachable
- Never train on test data, even "just to check something"
- Handle class imbalance — FLAT labels dominate; downsample or use class weights
